      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2023-04-27</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2023-05-11T16:56:34Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help Ensure Lower Patient Copays Act or the HELP Copays Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires health insurance plans to apply certain payments made by, or on behalf of, a plan enrollee toward a plan's cost-sharing requirements. Specifically, plans must apply third-party payments, financial assistance, discounts, product vouchers, and other reductions in out-of-pocket expenses toward the requirements.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
